values: God damn me and my dieing. Olivia is doign amazing. She keeps tugging my hair. It hurts! Damn her. I'm kidding, I love my little pookie. She's too cute!
I died again. Jetting back and forth for Olivia has been hard on me. I love her though.

It took forever for me to update but anyway... I'M A DADDY NOW! Olivia Mae Puget 3 lbs. 10 oz. 16 1/2 inches 10:36 PM She has dwarfism. A little scary, but I love her none the less. She has Davey's eyes. This is the best day of my life.
I'M GOING TO BE A DAD!

So. I've come to a decision. Davey and I are going to have a baby together. As friends. It was Davey's idea, and I was a little scared at first. But, after much thought, I've come to one conclusion..

I want to be a dad. And I want Davey to help.

We haven't even planted it in there and I'm pouring over baby name and pregnancy books.

Davey - IT SHALL <u>NOT</u> BE NAMED ERROL!



_le jade

Happy Easter all! I spent the latter part of theevening at my mom's house. Smith, Fritch and Gibson were there, too. I'm so effing stuffed.

I've talked to Rob, my fellow ninja fan, Bert, fellow lover of giant pickles, and Pierre, fellow younger brothers that suck person. And of course, my dearest Davey.


I heart all my friends.

Alright, I'm getting way too old to cart a 10 year old around the mall. I don't know what my mom has been feeding Gibson, but she needs to STOP! He's got WAY too much energy for his own good. Anywho, I'm Jade, I'm hot, you aren't, you should love me. Contact tastes like jade for a good time.
